FTT Format stdin to stdout with selected formatter.

	FromTextTo
	FormatToText
	FormatThisText
	FormatToTerminal
	FormaTTer
	ForTheText!

Build and run:

	$ ./build
	$ ./ftt -h
	$ ./ftt gph <stdin

Formatters:

	none	Default, only wrap lines according to -w and -t.
	gph	Gopher submenu
	gmi	Gemini text WIP
	... more to come, maybe?  I just need gph at the moment ('-')
